<h2 id="details">Details</h2>

<p>A vet, or a team chosen by a vet, can do the testing and assessment.&nbsp;</p>

<p>A farmer will not be eligible for funding unless you follow the guidance on:&nbsp;</p>

<p><a href="index">Poultry Biosecurity Review funding: guidance for poultry keepers and vets</a></p>
